<item>
            <title>[LU-9789] Create JobID prefix</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-9789</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Create JobID prefix to distinguish among clusters, or specific nodes within clusters (such as login nodes).&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;If a site has a single shared filesystem and multiple clusters/schedulers, it could be possible for a JobID to be insufficiently unique, or difficult to determine where the job ran.  Adding a small prefix would allow jobstats consumers a better understanding of where a job was run.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="47384">LU-9789</key>
