                            <comment id="259034" author="bevans" created="Mon, 2 Dec 2019 17:57:10 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Duplicate of &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-10698&quot; title=&quot;Specify complex JobIDs for Lustre&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-10698&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-10698&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="226026" author="gerrit" created="Fri, 13 Apr 2018 19:48:25 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Ben Evans (bevans@cray.com) uploaded a new patch: &lt;a href=&quot;https://review.whamcloud.com/31995&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://review.whamcloud.com/31995&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
